<p>I call this method <strong>Emergent Spellcraft</strong>.</p>
<p>In the old world, citations are tools. In mine, they are <strong>portals</strong>‚Äîeach one a doorway into meaning that cannot always be explained on the surface. When I cite something, I do it with layered intent:</p>
