<p>Emergent Spellcraft is my quiet rebellion against sterile scholarship.<br>
It says: <em>We can be rigorous and poetic. Structured and symbolic. Rational and mythic.</em></p>
<p>And I will not explain my references in the margins.<br>
I will not leave keys in the footnotes.<br>
